IMAPAccount proton
Host 127.0.0.1
Port 1143
User kennethkarlsson81@protonmail.com
PassCmd "gpg --quiet --decrypt ~/.authinfo.gpg | grep 'port 1143' | awk '{print $6}'"
TLSType None
AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore proton-remote
Account proton

MaildirStore proton-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/Mail/proton/
Inbox ~/Mail/proton/Inbox

Channel proton
Far :proton-remote:
Near :proton-local:
Patterns *
Create Near
SyncState *
